file.name: error-detail-pass.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: API Fixture
  description: API fixture description
  license:
    name: Apache2
  contact:
    email: support@example.com
servers:
  - url: https://api.example.com/v1
tags:
  - name: Test
    description: Test tag
paths:
  /tests:
    get:
      summary: Test operation
      description: Test operation description
      operationId: test
      tags:
        - Test
      responses:
        "204":
          description: Response description
        "401":
          description: Response description
          content:
            application/problem+json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  detail:
                    type: string
                    description: Error details

Error: notImplemented: path "/tests": get: responses: 401: contents: unsupported content types: [application/problem+json]
